  <my:Details>
    <my:Ship />
    <my:Number>S 01</my:Number>
    <my:Date>2015-05-15</my:Date>
    <my:Title>Bobcat Operation</my:Title>
  </my:Details>
  <my:Hazards>
    <my:Hazard my:HazardId="1">
      <my:Description>Environment - limited space</my:Description>
      <my:Severity>3</my:Severity>
      <my:Likelihood>3</my:Likelihood>
      <my:RiskFactor>5</my:RiskFactor>
      <my:ControlMeasures>a) Use of PPE; 
b) Use of high visibility vests; 
c) Proper illumination; 
d) Crew vigilance; 
d) Crew kept away until sufficient space; 
e) Careful driving by the bobcat operator; 
f) Bobcat movement signalling devices in good working condition.</my:ControlMeasures>
      <my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity>
      <my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood>
      <my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor>
    </my:Hazard>
    <my:Hazard my:HazardId="2">
      <my:Description>Crane - being struck by crane gear</my:Description>
      <my:Severity>3</my:Severity>
      <my:Likelihood>2</my:Likelihood>
      <my:RiskFactor>4</my:RiskFactor>
      <my:ControlMeasures>a) Proper illumination;
b) Post a person who will coordinate crane and bobcat movement;
c) If crane operator has his view obscured signaller to be posted (coordinator and signaller can be the same person);
d) When crane gear is being brought inside the cargo hold bobcat should retreat to give sufficient space for crane’s gear.</my:ControlMeasures>
      <my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity>
      <my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood>
      <my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor>
    </my:Hazard>
    <my:Hazard my:HazardId="3">
      <my:Description>Fumes - bobcat exhaust</my:Description>
      <my:Severity>3</my:Severity>
      <my:Likelihood>2</my:Likelihood>
      <my:RiskFactor>4</my:RiskFactor>
      <my:ControlMeasures>a) Open as many hatch covers as possible to allow suitable ventilation;
b) Consider use of holds mechanical ventilation; 
c) Bobcat should not be operated inside the cargo hold when all hatches are closed.</my:ControlMeasures>
      <my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity>
      <my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood>
      <my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor>
    </my:Hazard>
    <my:Hazard my:HazardId="4">
      <my:Description>Cargo - SWL of bobcat</my:Description>
      <my:Severity>3</my:Severity>
      <my:Likelihood>2</my:Likelihood>
      <my:RiskFactor>4</my:RiskFactor>
      <my:ControlMeasures>Care must be taken when working with heavy cargo, do not lift load greater than machine capacity otherwise it may tip forward.</my:ControlMeasures>
      <my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity>
      <my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood>
      <my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor>
    </my:Hazard>
    <my:Hazard my:HazardId="5">
      <my:Description>Bunker - vicinity of fuel tanks</my:Description>
      <my:Severity>3</my:Severity>
      <my:Likelihood>2</my:Likelihood>
      <my:RiskFactor>4</my:RiskFactor>
      <my:ControlMeasures>a) Proper illumination; 
b) Bobcat operator to be informed about tanks location and their content; 
c) Bobcat to be operated with great care by competent person.</my:ControlMeasures>
      <my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity>
      <my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood>
      <my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor>
    </my:Hazard>
    <my:Hazard my:HazardId="6">
      <my:Description>Machinery - failure - potential for electrocution</my:Description>
      <my:Severity>3</my:Severity>
      <my:Likelihood>2</my:Likelihood>
      <my:RiskFactor>4</my:RiskFactor>
      <my:ControlMeasures>a) Equipment to be checked prior to operation;
b) Bobcat must be in good working condition when in use, all electrical parts to be properly insulated; 
c) Maintenance / inspections as per manufacturer’s manual, Company MPM system.</my:ControlMeasures>
      <my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity>
      <my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood>
      <my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor>
    </my:Hazard>
    <my:Hazard my:HazardId="7">
      <my:Description>Crewmember being unsighted by the bobcat driver - Struck/Crushed</my:Description>
      <my:Severity>3</my:Severity>
      <my:Likelihood>3</my:Likelihood>
      <my:RiskFactor>5</my:RiskFactor>
      <my:ControlMeasures>Crew members to pay attention at all the times at the movement of the bobcat.</my:ControlMeasures>
      <my:ReducedSeverity>3</my:ReducedSeverity>
      <my:ReducedLikelihood>1</my:ReducedLikelihood>
      <my:ReducedRiskFactor>3</my:ReducedRiskFactor>
    </my:Hazard>
  </my:Hazards>
